[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/99/299900.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1538450","time":"2019-12-16 05:56","userId":"299900","userName":"Oshino","userSign":"","message":"<a href=\"http://bgm.tv/ep/773906\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">卫宫家的汉堡肉</a><br><br>这道菜的要点总结：<br>-洋葱的处理：一半小火煎至内部的糖焦化提供甜味、一半直接加入保留口感<br>-面包糠的量应该与洋葱持平，否则肉饼不成形无法承受拍打<br>-烹饪的思路和煎饺相同：两面都煎过之后，加入少量料汁焖煎直至蒸干以防糊底<br>-原汤化原食：肉饼出锅后不洗锅，加入糯米酒（或任何手边有的酒）及喜欢的调味小火收浓稠<br><br>西式做法为了保留肉的嫩感、多汁感选择不全熟，对于我的吃不来生肉的亚洲味觉来说，还是用洋葱、有锁水力的面包糠、加汁焖煎在保证全熟的同时鲜嫩多汁的日式做法更下饭","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/71/337184.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1538499","time":"2019-12-16 12:30","userId":"337184","userName":"haveatry","userSign":"","message":"好奇怪哦，这层报社都不带图的。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/99/299900.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1538519","time":"2019-12-16 14:18","userId":"299900","userName":"Oshino","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">haveatry</span> 说: 好奇怪哦，这层报社都不带图的。</q></div><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">没你的图好看没好意思放</span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/71/337184.jpg","floor":"#2-3","id":"1538529","time":"2019-12-16 15:16","userId":"337184","userName":"haveatry","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Oshino</span> 说: 没你的图好看没好意思放</q></div>届不到届不到，我太惨了 ~~"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/23/272356.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1538535","time":"2019-12-16 15:49","userId":"nihilum890","userName":"Nihilum890","userSign":"(今夜无眠)","message":"不如看看马壮实做没做过这道菜","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/71/337184.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1538541","time":"2019-12-16 16:04","userId":"337184","userName":"haveatry","userSign":"","message":"这道菜只需要十分钟，还蛮简单的 ~~~"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/33/42/334255.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1539308","time":"2019-12-18 23:44","userId":"334255","userName":"烧鳗事变🔮","userSign":"","message":"✌️（ˉ﹃ˉ）&#x1F44D;",